item.title: Need help with compiler for server
item.dc:creator: @jjones10 jjones10
item.description:
@jjones10 wrote:

Okay, go to your compiler and erase everything and post: @echo off title HellzEnd Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_03\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java @echo HellzEnd succesfully compiled! pause

next go to your computer C:\program files\java
and look what type of jdk you have.

next replace where it says "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_03\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java

replace C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_03\bin\javac.exe with your version of jdk
